Package neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.demo

Contains examples of using the Neustar Java Toolkit.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DomainCheckDemo
    A basic demonstration of the life cycle of a SessionManager using a Domain Check Command.
    DomainCreateWithExtensionDemo
    A demonstration of the steps required to perform a domain create utilising the SECDNS extension.
    DomainInfoWithExtensionDemo
    A demonstration of the steps required to perform a domain info, with the response returning extension elements.
    PipeliningDemo
    A demonstration of the steps required to pipeline a series of commands through a session manager.

Package neustar.registry.jtoolkit2.demo Description

Contains examples of using the Neustar Java Toolkit. These include:
  1. Domain Check
  2. Domain Create with extensions
  3. Domain Info with extensions
  4. Command Pipelining
.
